---
import Container from "../ui/Container.astro";
---

<section class="pb-20 sm:pb-24">
  <Container>
    <div
      class="editorial-grid relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-primary-soft bg-primary-soft-2 px-7 py-10 sm:px-12 sm:py-14"
    >
      <span
        class="absolute right-10 top-8 hidden rounded-lg bg-surface px-4 py-2 font-mono text-xs text-primary sm:block"
      >
        git push origin main
      </span>
      <p
        class="font-mono text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary"
      >
        Ikut dari awal
      </p>
      <h2
        class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-5xl"
      >
        Bantu Sakala jadi jalur deploy yang ramah untuk belajar.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-muted">
        Lihat arahnya, baca dokumentasinya, dan bantu bentuk pengalaman deploy
        yang jelas untuk project kecil.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-9 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a
          href="/docs"
          class="rounded-xl bg-primary px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-primary-dark"
        >
          Baca Dokumentasi
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/gmedia"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
          class="rounded-xl border border-primary bg-surface px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-primary hover:bg-background"
        >
          Lihat GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
